name: ODE TO SINEAD O'CONNOR
description: I adore recording artist, Sinead O'Connor with all being. Ever since I was young I've always admired her bravery in music, against the Catholic Church, in her personal life, and much more. She's been through so much in life; the good and the bad. But, one of the things I noticed as a youth was that if you added a K and an H to her name it spells out skinhead. What makes this even more interesting was that for much of her career, she had a crew cut (close to being shaved completely off). This part needs to be emphasized...obviously, Sinead is NOT a skinhead (a person who associates with a group that commits hooliganism or street violence or that holds white supremacist or anti-immigrant views.) I love you Sinead and I wish you continued success, mental wellness, and I truly hope you find lasting love, you deserve it! You're an amazing human and your journey goes on.
